I always stay outside for battles,

574
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,920
and I even slept on the ground before.

575
00:34:41,040 --> 00:34:41,710
It's all the same to me.

576
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:42,920
But you are different.

577
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:45,190
So you should sleep on the bed.

578
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:25,580
♪Among the clouds drifting away,
white birds warble riding wind♪

579
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,900
♪Leaning against the willow,
I view the green hills by the waterside♪

580
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:34,060
♪Gently, you hang about
in the vicinity of my heart♪

581
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:39,860
♪Spring coming after winter,
warm breeze ripples the river♪

582
00:35:40,980 --> 00:35:43,540
♪In the courtyard, flowers
are blooming under the full moon♪

583
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:49,220
♪Starlight is like sparrow
while you are like a wild goose♪

584
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:54,260
♪The blue sky♪

585
00:35:55,100 --> 00:35:58,020
♪And the lake in the eyes♪

586
00:35:58,780 --> 00:36:04,900
♪Look like scroll paintings
what is reflected in them is your face♪

587
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:08,820
♪As the whale longs for the sea♪

588
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:12,300
♪I yearn for you♪

589
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:15,440
I didn't care about you enough before.

590
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,240
Actually,

591
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,240
you've always treated me well.

592
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:23,740
♪My spotless heart enjoys the company of
the eternal moon light♪

593
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:26,580
♪Our mutual devotion to each other,
bears witness to the lapse of time♪

594
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:27,760
From now on,

595
00:36:29,040 --> 00:36:29,560
I won't let you

596
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:31,120
get hurt anymore.

597
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:33,500
♪And I am blended with you
by our attachment to each other♪

598
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:39,300
♪The grass and trees
choose the drifting clouds♪

599
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:42,940
♪I feel lucky to have been chosen by you♪

600
00:36:43,580 --> 00:36:47,500
♪The enduring rock equals the jade
which boasts such luster♪

601
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:53,980
♪With things constantly changing♪

602
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:57,420
♪Whose love will last forever♪

603
00:36:58,420 --> 00:37:03,700
♪When we met, the answer
came to mind♪

604
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:44,620
(The Waterway Classic)

605
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:54,760
Did I wake you up?

606
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:00,920
I wasn't asleep either.

607
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:07,880
Are you

608
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,320
reading The Waterway Classic?

609
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,320
I just read it to kill time.

610
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:19,880
I want to read

611
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,960
the fishing songs, folk songs,

612
00:38:22,080 --> 00:38:23,120
and fairy tales in the book,

613
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:26,480
hoping one day I'll have a chance

614
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:28,600
to...

615
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:32,960
To what?

616
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:38,120
...to take a look at those sceneries.

617
00:38:43,140 --> 00:38:44,060
(The Waterway Classic)

618
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:47,360
I happen

619
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:49,920
to hold the same thought.

620
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,520
I won't disturb you anymore.

621
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,480
Go to sleep.

622
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:33,600
Put your hands under the blanket.

623
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,720
Don't.

624
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:23,760
Don't.

625
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:26,720
Don't.

626
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,440
(Nightmare again?)

627
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,600
Don't.

628
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,760
Don't.

629
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:37,560
Run.

630
00:40:38,200 --> 00:40:38,920
Run.

631
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,200
Run.

632
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:08,880
General Fu.

633
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,280
I see that you are very good at combat.

634
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,000
When did you start

635
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:12,200
to learn martial arts?

636
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:13,800
For His Lordship's health benefits,

637
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,320
the late Marquis started teaching

638
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,320
him martial arts when he was little.

639
00:41:17,560 --> 00:41:18,840
I also lived in the mansion,

640
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:20,320
so I practiced together with him.

641
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:22,840
When he was little?

642
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,240
In that case,

643
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,760
you've been with His Lordship
for many years.

644
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:27,720
You must know His Lordship very well.

645
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:29,080
My mother passed away early.

646
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:31,120
I've kept His Lordship company
when I was a child.

647
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,880
Great Madam treated me like her son.

648
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,760
I practiced martial arts

649
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,720
and joined the army with him.

650
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,040
So, I know everything

651
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:38,520
about His Lordship.

652
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,440
I found

653
00:41:42,560 --> 00:41:44,520
that His Lordship always has nightmares.

654
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,480
Dreams are reflections of reality.

655
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:48,880
But His Lordship is
such a strong and tough man.

656
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:50,560
What bothers him

657
00:41:50,680 --> 00:41:51,920
this much exactly?

658
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:53,520
Although it's been years,

659
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:55,400
His Lordship still can't let go of

660
00:41:55,560 --> 00:41:56,640
a matter that happened in the past.

661
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,960
Happened in the past?

662
00:41:58,120 --> 00:41:59,520
Back then, late Marquis,
and Master Ling'an

663
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:00,920
fell into the trap set up by Ou family

664
00:42:01,080 --> 00:42:02,000
and got killed on the battleground.

665
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:03,200
And I also lost my father

666
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,560
at that time.

667
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:05,720
From then on, I became

668
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,760
His Lordship's Vice General.

669
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:08,680
We suffered great loss in that battle,

670
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,560
which almost wiped out the entire army.

671
00:42:11,200 --> 00:42:12,680
I guess His Lordship
still can't forget that.

672
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,440
For all these years,

673
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,800
His Lordship must have gone

674
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,760
through so many brutal battles

675
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,320
for today's

676
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,360
peace and prosperity of Xu family.

677
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,040
After late Marquis passed away,

678
00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:25,600
Ou family set us up

679
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:27,800
and almost destroyed Xu family.

680
00:42:28,040 --> 00:42:29,720
Marquis Jingyuan kept pushing us.

681
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:32,160
So His Lordship took me
to join the army.

682
00:42:32,520 --> 00:42:33,480
He started from an ordinary soldier

683
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:34,640
and made his way up step by step.

684
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:35,840
To make contributions,

685
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,240
His Lordship fought enemies bravely

686
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,480
and gave no thought to his own safety.

687
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:39,800
One day,

688
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:40,800
the commander sent us

689
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:42,040
to secretly attack the enemy's camp.

690
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:48,000
Young Master,

691
00:42:48,160 --> 00:42:49,080
have you lost your mind?

692
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:50,520
There are so many enemies,

693
00:42:50,520 --> 00:42:51,560
yet we only have a dozen people.

694
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:52,760
We are literally looking for death.

695
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:53,760
Of course I realize that.

696
00:42:54,680 --> 00:42:55,520
But hundreds of lives

697
00:42:55,640 --> 00:42:56,920
of our Xu family

698
00:42:56,920 --> 00:42:58,160
count on me now.

699
00:42:58,600 --> 00:42:59,640
If I don't make this contribution,

700
00:43:00,200 --> 00:43:01,760
our Xu family will never
be able to turn over,

701
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:03,880
and we can never
take down the Ou family

702
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,480
and avenge my father
and my brother.

703
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:11,920
I have to take this risk

704
00:43:12,360 --> 00:43:13,520
even if I die.

705
00:43:26,240 --> 00:43:27,920
His Lordship has gone through a lot.

706
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:29,800
But he always
keeps everything to himself.

707
00:43:30,480 --> 00:43:31,520
Over time,

708
00:43:31,880 --> 00:43:33,320
he's become a little cold

709
00:43:33,480 --> 00:43:34,440
and ruthless.

710
00:43:35,480 --> 00:43:36,320
But I know

711
00:43:36,560 --> 00:43:38,040
that this is his way to protect

712
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:39,960
Xu family and himself.

713
00:43:42,360 --> 00:43:43,240
So,

714
00:43:43,400 --> 00:43:45,280
that's why His Lordship appears

715
00:43:45,680 --> 00:43:46,720
to be cold and serious.

716
00:43:47,760 --> 00:43:49,480
But he wasn't like that before.

717
00:43:49,840 --> 00:43:51,240
When the late Marquis was still alive,

718
00:43:51,400 --> 00:43:52,160
His Lordship liked laughing

719
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:53,160
and playing polo.

720
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:54,000
He was nothing different

721
00:43:54,160 --> 00:43:54,800
from those lively and cheerful

722
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:56,000
young men in the capital.

723
00:43:57,960 --> 00:44:00,080
A lively and cheerful Marquis?

724
00:44:02,480 --> 00:44:03,960
It's really hard to imagine.

725
00:44:17,920 --> 00:44:19,120
(For all these years,)

726
00:44:19,680 --> 00:44:21,480
(His Lordship has gone through a lot.)

727
00:44:22,120 --> 00:44:23,800
(But he always
keeps everything to himself.)

728
00:44:24,680 --> 00:44:25,760
(Over time,)

729
00:44:26,600 --> 00:44:28,360
(he's armed himself)

730
00:44:29,240 --> 00:44:31,160
(with coldness and ruthlessness.)

731
00:44:41,400 --> 00:44:42,480
My Lord, you are back.

732
00:44:42,840 --> 00:44:43,920
Why are you still up?

733
00:44:45,320 --> 00:44:46,600
I made some soup for you.

734
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:48,520
It'll warm you up.

735
00:45:06,080 --> 00:45:06,760
My Lord.

736
00:45:10,360 --> 00:45:12,320
I strained my wrist

737
00:45:12,480 --> 00:45:13,560
when I practiced sword today.

738
00:45:14,080 --> 00:45:15,560
It still feels sore.

739
00:45:15,960 --> 00:45:18,400
Shiyi, could you do me a favor?

740
00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:26,520
You are pretending it, aren't you?

741
00:45:27,640 --> 00:45:28,880
It's true.

742
00:45:29,320 --> 00:45:30,080
I'm not lying.

743
00:45:33,040 --> 00:45:34,400
Then I'll go get some medicine.

744
00:45:51,120 --> 00:45:52,640
My Lord, do you want the soup or not?

745
00:46:31,120 --> 00:46:31,680
Let me.

746
00:46:58,380 --> 00:47:01,220
♪In the cold darkness of midnight,
a sigh is heard♪

747
00:47:01,820 --> 00:47:04,620
♪Who picked up the paintbrush
to draw loneliness♪

748
00:47:05,940 --> 00:47:12,500
♪In my life, I can draw everything,
but lovesickness♪

749
00:47:12,820 --> 00:47:14,980
♪The mountain city is waiting for rain♪

750
00:47:15,980 --> 00:47:19,580
♪I am waiting for you
to pass in my memory♪

751
00:47:20,020 --> 00:47:26,180
♪The sky is in a more lonely color
than your face♪

752
00:47:26,620 --> 00:47:29,140
♪The wind rises
and the candle light flickers♪

753
00:47:29,940 --> 00:47:32,620
♪The thin clothes
can't stand the cold days♪

754
00:47:33,820 --> 00:47:40,660
♪Full of twists and turns,
fate is untold♪

755
00:47:41,060 --> 00:47:43,260
♪I ground my thoughts into ink♪

756
00:47:44,260 --> 00:47:47,700
♪But I still can't sketch your contours♪

757
00:47:48,220 --> 00:47:53,980
♪How could the ink
and paper exhaust our stories♪

758
00:47:54,820 --> 00:48:01,700
♪Who picked up the pen
to disturb the heart♪

759
00:48:01,780 --> 00:48:08,700
♪Who visited to remind me of the past♪

760
00:48:08,980 --> 00:48:12,420
♪If feelings can be kept in mind,
but cannot be confessed♪

761
00:48:13,700 --> 00:48:15,980
♪I won't escape from whatever end♪

762
00:48:17,300 --> 00:48:23,020
♪In the dim lantern light,
with you there is me♪

763
00:48:23,020 --> 00:48:29,940
♪Who picked up the pen
to set free lonely tears♪

764
00:48:30,180 --> 00:48:36,700
♪Whoever visited my life,
only you stayed all the days♪

765
00:48:37,260 --> 00:48:40,780
♪If the moth doesn't fly into the fire♪

766
00:48:41,860 --> 00:48:44,820
♪How can it be said to be persistent♪

767
00:48:45,300 --> 00:48:52,940
♪Coming to the end of your story,
there is me♪
